@DefaultQualifier(org.checkerframework.checker.nullness.qual.NonNull.class)

Package org.spongepowered.configurate.extra.dfu.v4

Implementation of DataFixerUpper interfaces for Configurate types.

This version of DataFixerUpper is used in Minecraft 1.16.2 onwards.

This module is also compatible with DataFixerUpper v5, since there were no major API changes.

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConfigurateOps
    Implementation of DataFixerUpper's DynamicOps.
    ConfigurateOpsBuilder
    A builder for ConfigurateOps instances.
    DataFixerTransformation
    A transformation that exposes a single DataFixer to a configuration in a friendly way.
    DataFixerTransformation.Builder
    Builder for DataFixerTransformation.
    DfuSerializers
    A bridge between Configurate and DataFixerUpper serialization types.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ConfigurateOps.Protection
    Protection level for configuration node accesses through ops instance.
